high_descs: Move to the arm chair closet to the door
Pick up the keys from the chair
Move to the coffee table to the right of you
Place the keys on the table
Move to the shelf to the right and behind you
Pick up the keys from the counter
Move to the coffee table to the left of you
Place the keys on the table
anns.task_desc: Put two sets of keys on the coffee table.

high_descs: Walk straight, turn left and walk over to the armchair.
Pick up the keys off of the chair.
Turn around and the turn left and walk to the coffee table.
Set the keys on the coffee table.
Turn around and walk to the bookcase on the wall.
Pick up the keys from the top of the bookcase.
Walk back to the coffee table.
Set the keys onto the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Put both sets of keys on the coffee table.

high_descs: Go forward to the wall, hang a left and go to the wall, go right to the shelf, hang a left, go right into the living room, then go to the first chair on your left.
Pick up the keys that are on the chair.
Turn around and go to the shelf, then hang a left and go to the table that is in front of the couch.
Put the keys on the right side of the table.
Turn around and go to the wall, go to the left to the shelf with the tissues on it.
Pick up the keys that are behind the tissues on the shelf.
Go the the left, then hang a right and go to the table that is in front of the couch.
Put the keys on the table to the left of the other set of keys.
anns.task_desc: Put two sets of keys on a table.
